{"tid":2160474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"四川暴雨淹車 航班延誤破紀錄","createTime":"2020-08-17T03:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T04:25:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7fc179acd1c5b9b5a6a648dec23083b0ccb12f","tid":2160474,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T03:41:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200817/UETZCA4TMVBGNJLKZ72BBPJOZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200817%2FUETZCA4TMVBGNJLKZ72BBPJOZI%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=47d2b5fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200817%2FUETZCA4TMVBGNJLKZ72BBPJOZI%2F&h=c72955b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200817/UETZCA4TMVBGNJLKZ72BBPJOZI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n四川暴雨淹車 航班延誤破紀錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YQnHt--vbYwJOeykJDBVQS9NCBI=/640x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5T45H3C65FGAND2WH5L7Y4I2ZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYQnHt--vbYwJOeykJDBVQS9NCBI%3D%2F640x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5T45H3C65FGAND2WH5L7Y4I2ZI.jpg&h=a6e050c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■成都低窪道路昨被水淹，汽車淹沒。<br />\n<br />\n持續了一個月的四川盤地雨災持續，上周末（15日）開始的新一輪強降雨導致四川31條江河出現超警超保水位，多地農田、交通、水利等基礎設施受損，綿陽、成都、廣元、德陽緊急疏散六萬多人，省會成都市因暴雨交通大受影響，多條高速公路關閉或限行，成都雙流國際機場至少有234班航班取消，是當地今年最嚴重的航班延誤事件。<br />\n<br />\n前天早上8時起的24小時內，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長江水位超警戒<br />\n<br />\n受強降雨影響，長江上游嘉陵江支流涪江小河壩站昨午已超過238米的警戒水位，水利部長江水利委員會水文局昨發佈「嘉陵江2020年第2號洪水」已經形成。<br />\n<br />\n新華社/中新社"},{"pid":"30579533152476dd15cf869879f8c4e87c93ae20","tid":2160474,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"好多財呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57100b2764635433e30bbab5f32d80e487afe667","tid":2160474,"uid":189564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zgTPAGv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzgTPAGv.gif&h=91c3a658&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"827f540dc9676888351dae2eb5f4802c0cd967c3","tid":2160474,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:18:17.000Z","msg":"為四川人民消消暑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5e095f502a11ec0cf7ac83428bbcbbbdd4af67","tid":2160474,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"車呢? <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13172fa612bbeb1d676ad77a6b9b44194bd0195c","tid":2160474,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"夏水禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}